desc replaces the description of how long the modifier lasts

add a modifier to a unit
add_province_modifier = { name = name days/months/years=x mode = add/extend/replace/add_and_extend <size = x> <desc = string>}
desc replaces the description of how long the modifier lasts

add a modifier to a rebel
